{"tid":686919,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"柴灣IVE男主管涉非禮女下屬遭舉報　暫未有人被捕","createTime":"2018-06-01T17:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T07:11:11.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ee01a40c8413a508fede024945329c4dd047d952","tid":686919,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T17:30:35.000Z","msg":"職業訓練局轄下的香港專業教育學院（IVE）柴灣分校爆出懷疑風化案，一名男主管級人員涉嫌性侵犯女下屬，受害人啞忍多年，直至在去年底在facebook公開事件，引起校內討論。警方表示，上月29日接獲一名40歲女子報案，指於2014年在柴灣區懷疑被一名男子非禮，交由東區警區重案組第二隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n有自稱是職訓局職員的人士向東網表示，一名男主管級人員涉嫌非禮女下屬。據悉，該名女受害人曾向多方面求助，包括職訓局高層，但不得要領。該名職員表示希望事件公開後，校方可嚴肅及認真處理，還女受害人一個公道。職訓局回應指，有既定員工投訴政策，並會按相關程序處理。"},{"pid":"411d5b4906a9f944e8787782a8337b7deb966aa0","tid":686919,"uid":75847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T17:43:57.000Z","msg":"40歲女子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178da6b623d0177ce03156877d83d7aaf612f8fa","tid":686919,"uid":3936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T18:24:17.000Z","msg":"2014年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db2e6f571c88d6b206feab32d90ac208a7c8c52","tid":686919,"uid":161656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T07:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好 <br />\n#me too 就唔洗做<br />\n政府機構又炒唔到<br />\n轉個頭又話精神病<br />\n返工又得 唔返工又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾爽皮"},{"pid":"1c168fbb14ead36e6c7e03e0aade1d576f25d0db","tid":686919,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T07:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2966e76ebbb70083878cd3460b23b7f235b764d","tid":686919,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T07:10:26.000Z","msg":"屌 仲以為香港可以得分 唔洗衰俾